This project was created to help developers work with Telerik Grid for ASP.NET MVC coupled with some mapping techniques to convert Entities objects into ViewModels objects.

If you're one of us, you have to implement CustomBinding in order to query the database reporting some criteria for sort, group and filter the income data, and then convert back the result to a list of ViewModels.

Sounds simple, but can become a very complicated and repetitive task.

So TelerikMvcGridCustomBindingHelper was built in order to automate this process in a very smooth way.
summary: This project was created to help developers work with Telerik Grid for ASP.NET MVC coupled with some mapping techniques to convert Entities objects into ViewModels objects.

Mongol is a wrapper for the MongoDB Official C# Driver which makes it very easy to create repository pattern classes around strongly typed collections for POCO objects.  
    Mongol also includes lambda-based property name resolution for building MongoDB Query/Update operations without magic strings.
summary:
QuickStart:
    1. Install Nuget Package
    2. Set Mongol.Url appSetting with mongodb:// url
    3. Create POCO classes, and mark with [BsonId]
    4. Use instances of RecordManager<TClass> to perform basic repository operations.
    5. Extend RecordManager<TClass> to encapsulate operations for Query/Update using inherited methods, or directly access the collection.

Please visit developer.intuit.com for more information on getting started.  Support is available through our forums at idnforums.intuit.com.  *** Visual Studio must be run with Administrator privileges before installing this package, as it makes changes to the IDE.  After successful installation, please restart Visual Studio to see the Intuit Anywhere Add-in in your toolbar. ***
summary: Windows Azure SDK 2.0 for Intuit Partner Platform

This project was created to help developers work with Telerik Grid for ASP.NET MVC coupled with some mapping techniques to convert Entities objects into ViewModels objects.

If you're one of us, you have to implement CustomBinding in order to query the database reporting some criteria for sort, group and filter the income data, and then convert back the result to a list of ViewModels.

Sounds simple, but can become a very complicated and repetitive task.

So TelerikMvcGridCustomBindingHelper was built in order to automate this process in a very smooth way.
summary: This project was created to help developers work with Telerik Grid for ASP.NET MVC coupled with some mapping techniques to convert Entities objects into ViewModels objects.

Working with dates and time in .NET works great, but I feel it could be more natural to work with them. new DateTime(2000, 6, 3) is less natural than 3.June(2000), isn't it?
summary:
The DateTime and Timespan Structs of the .net framework are somewhat awkward to work with, this api helps to make code more readable, for example: 
var today = 23.February(1990).At(3.AM());
